# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:15
translate chinese tammy3_57a68160:

    # tm "Today we're going to learn about grappling."
    tm "今天我们要学习地面缠斗。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:16
translate chinese tammy3_8bbac2a1:

    # tm "In a fight, 90 percent of the time the two combatants will end up on the mat."
    tm "在实战中，90%的情况下双方都会倒在垫子上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:17
translate chinese tammy3_ac91ad7e:

    # tm "When that happens, you need to know how to grapple, or you'll get a limb broken or get choked out."
    tm "一旦发生这种情况，你必须懂得地面缠斗，否则要么断肢，要么被勒昏过去。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:18
translate chinese tammy3_d672444d:

    # pc "What if I just don't go to the ground."
    pc "那我干脆不倒地不就好了？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:19
translate chinese tammy3_ad2a727b:

    # tm "Not an option."
    tm "没门。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:20
translate chinese tammy3_3b2e0784:

    # pc "Sure it is, if I don't want you to take me to the ground--"
    pc "当然可以，如果我不想让你把我拖到地上的话——"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:23
translate chinese tammy3_d5995587:

    # "What was I saying? All thought is knocked out of my mind as Tammy slams into me like a bullet."
    "我刚才说什么来着？塔米像子弹般猛扑过来，瞬间让我脑中一片空白。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:24
translate chinese tammy3_6c3dcce2:

    # "I feel myself falling backwards."
    "我感觉自己向后倒去。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:27
translate chinese tammy3_2f96182c:

    # "Then I hit the mat hard. Tammy is on top of me in an instant."
    "接着重重摔在垫子上。塔米瞬间压在我身上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:28
translate chinese tammy3_c46fa0c1:

    # pc "Ouch."
    pc "哎哟。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:29
translate chinese tammy3_cd6347a1:

    # tm "Now you're on the ground and you can't do anything."
    tm "现在你躺在地上，什么都做不了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:32
translate chinese tammy3_dae4a999:

    # "I attempt to push her off me, but I can't get any leverage from the position I'm in."
    "我试图把她推开，但这个姿势让我完全无法施力。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:33
translate chinese tammy3_81be8aeb:

    # tm "Not going to happen."
    tm "没门。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:35
translate chinese tammy3_a4fdb823:

    # tm "Good, I'm glad you understand."
    tm "好，很高兴你明白了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:37
translate chinese tammy3_03220617:

    # tm "Focus. Pretend I'm a 200-pound hairy man."
    tm "集中注意力。假装我是个200磅重的毛茸茸大汉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:38
translate chinese tammy3_6d1ff706:

    # pc "I'd rather not."
    pc "我还是算了吧。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:39
translate chinese tammy3_938b0434:

    # tm "This position is called a full mount."
    tm "这个姿势叫“完全压制”。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:40
translate chinese tammy3_ba765fb2:

    # tm "I have my knees bracing myself on both sides of your body and I keep your back pressed against the mat."
    tm "我的双膝抵在你身体两侧，把你背部死死压在垫子上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:41
translate chinese tammy3_c6c5a568:

    # tm "It negates all of your strength and puts me in a position where I can do pretty much whatever I want."
    tm "这会让你完全丧失力量，而我则处于可以为所欲为的地位。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:44
translate chinese tammy3_04908dac:

    # tm "See. Nothing you can do to stop me."
    tm "看吧。你根本无力阻止我。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:47
translate chinese tammy3_d9fe7a04:

    # tm "I'm a 200-pound hairy man, remember?"
    tm "我是那个200磅重的毛茸茸大汉，记得吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:48
translate chinese tammy3_7c4a85b3:

    # pc "My imagination is not that good."
    pc "我的想象力没那么丰富。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:50
translate chinese tammy3_65ea559e:

    # tm "Sorry, you're right. I'll focus on the fighting."
    tm "抱歉，你说得对。我还是专注于格斗吧。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:53
translate chinese tammy3_9e2865cc:

    # tm "Okay, let's switch positions now. You're on top and I'm on bottom."
    tm "好，现在换个姿势。你在上，我在下。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:56
translate chinese tammy3_90afe576:

    # "She lies down on her back and allows me to get on top of her."
    "她仰面躺下，让我趴在她身上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:57
translate chinese tammy3_c97236f5:

    # tm "You can use your full weight, it's okay. I can take it."
    tm "你可以用全身的重量，没关系。我扛得住。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:58
translate chinese tammy3_66eb4b07:

    # tm "Okay, now I want you to do your best to hold me in this position and I'll show you how to escape it."
    tm "好，现在我要你尽全力把我固定在这个位置，我会教你如何脱身。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:61
translate chinese tammy3_d4c215db:

    # "She grabs my arm and then suddenly slams her hips upwards."
    "她抓住我的手臂，然后突然猛地向上顶起臀部。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:64
translate chinese tammy3_b72fcb07:

    # "Then she rolls, knocking me onto my back once again."
    "接着她翻身，又把我掀翻在背上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:65
translate chinese tammy3_d9c1adb2:

    # tm "See? Easy."
    tm "看？很简单。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:66
translate chinese tammy3_6a40f515:

    # tm "You just grab the arm to stop the person on top from posting up with it."
    tm "你只要抓住对方的手臂，阻止上面的人用它撑起身体。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:67
translate chinese tammy3_46422fcf:

    # tm "You slam your hips upwards to create space, then roll."
    tm "你猛地向上顶起臀部创造空间，然后翻身。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:68
translate chinese tammy3_e870d3d9:

    # tm "Got it?"
    tm "明白了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:69
translate chinese tammy3_1e770403:

    # pc "I think so."
    pc "我想我明白了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:70
translate chinese tammy3_d4d7a636:

    # tm "Let's practice."
    tm "我们来练习一下。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:73
translate chinese tammy3_72164a62:

    # "We return to the previous position."
    "我们回到之前的姿势。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:74
translate chinese tammy3_a8e28fcc:

    # "Then I do what she said. I grab her arm and slam my hips upwards, then roll."
    "接着我照她说的做。我抓住她的手臂，猛地向上顶起臀部，然后翻身。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:75
translate chinese tammy3_b74e68d2:

    # "It takes a couple of tries to get the movements right, but then..."
    "试了几次才把动作做对，但随后……"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:78
translate chinese tammy3_004dfbf8:

    # "I knock her on her back and I'm on top of her."
    "我把她掀翻在背上，自己压在了她身上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:79
translate chinese tammy3_591f67d4:

    # tm "That was perfect! Good job!"
    tm "太完美了！干得漂亮！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:80
translate chinese tammy3_7d946eb7:

    # pc "Thanks. I think I got it."
    pc "谢谢。我觉得我掌握了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:81
translate chinese tammy3_7c97e1b9:

    # tm "Now that you got me in this position, you could do a lot of different things to me."
    tm "既然你把我压在这个位置，你可以对我做很多不同的动作。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:84
translate chinese tammy3_e35118d4:

    # tm "Right now, you're in what we call closed guard."
    tm "现在，你处于我们所谓的封闭式护卫位。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:85
translate chinese tammy3_14f2bacf:

    # tm "You could pass into a half-guard, or even a full mount."
    tm "你可以突破到半护卫位，甚至完全压制位。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:86
translate chinese tammy3_4b84023a:

    # tm "You could go for a leg-hold. Or you could just stand up and go back to trading blows."
    tm "你可以尝试锁腿。或者你也可以直接站起来，回到互殴状态。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:88
translate chinese tammy3_9e4a79ed:

    # tm "Oh yeah?"
    tm "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:89
translate chinese tammy3_ecca25fc:

    # tm "I think I can guess what you're thinking about."
    tm "我觉得我能猜到你在想什么。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:90
translate chinese tammy3_ba505d9b:

    # tm "You're really going to have to start wearing a cup when we do this."
    tm "下次练这个的时候，你真的得戴上护裆了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:91
translate chinese tammy3_ef242433:

    # tm "I can see pretty much your whole thing flopping around there."
    tm "我几乎能看到你那玩意儿在那儿晃来晃去。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:92
translate chinese tammy3_b2395364:

    # pc "Sorry."
    pc "抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:93
translate chinese tammy3_532ec656:

    # tm "Nah, it's alright."
    tm "没关系，没事的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:94
translate chinese tammy3_54238a64:

    # tm "Okay, let me up."
    tm "好了，放我起来。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:98
translate chinese tammy3_742a8c61:

    # tm "You did good today. We'll keep practicing and teach you more grappling and you'll get even better."
    tm "你今天表现不错。我们会继续练习，教你更多的地面缠斗技巧，你会变得更厉害的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:101
translate chinese tammy3_00868774:

    # tm "You're welcome."
    tm "不客气。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:104
translate chinese tammy3_6ce6700e:

    # tm "I had fun too. Any time you want to roll around, you just let me know."
    tm "我也玩得很开心。随时想练就告诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:105
translate chinese tammy3_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "我会找你的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:106
translate chinese tammy3_efc77bf1:

    # tm "Alright, well I'm going to wash up and head out."
    tm "行，那我洗个澡就走了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:107
translate chinese tammy3_63a1cf3a:

    # tm "I'll see you next time, [pcname]."
    tm "下次见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:108
translate chinese tammy3_67f3ea81:

    # pc "Okay. Bye, Tammy."
    pc "好的。再见，塔米。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:109
translate chinese tammy3_15a8a240:

    # "With that, I go to the showers and clean up, then leave the gym."
    "说完，我便去淋浴间冲洗，然后离开了健身房。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:2
    old "After Tammy invites you to come train MMA with her,"
    new "在塔米邀请你和她一起练习综合格斗之后，"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:3
    old "go to the gym on the weekend in the morning or afternoon and choose to train MMA."
    new "周末的上午或下午去健身房，并选择练习综合格斗。"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:31
    old "Knock her off of you"
    new "把她从你身上撂下来"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:34
    old "Okay you proved your point"
    new "行吧，你证明了你的观点"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:36
    old "Oh, this is kind of nice."
    new "哦，这感觉还挺不错的。"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:46
    old "Why would I want to?"
    new "我为什么要这么做？"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:49
    old "Hey, that's not cool"
    new "嘿，这可不太好"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:83
    old "Like what?"
    new "比如什么？"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:87
    old "I could think of a few things"
    new "我能想到几件事"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:100
    old "Thanks for teaching me"
    new "谢谢你教我"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy3.rpy:102
    old "Yeah it was fun rolling around with you"
    new "是啊，跟你打打滚挺有意思的"

